item.title: FAQ
item.description: Welcome to our dental office! We are committed to providing comprehensive and professional dental care to our patients. Below, you will find some frequently asked questions that may help you better understand our offerings and procedures. If you have additional questions or need further information, feel free to contact our team. Thank you for trusting and choosing our dental office. 1. What are the opening hours of the dental office? Our dental office is open from Monday to Friday, from 10:00 AM to 8:00 PM.
